Germany Approved Sale of 24 Howitzers to Qatar, Bild Reports

-- B y   C o r n e l i u s   R a h n
-- 
2011-07-17T12:20:24Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-17/germany-approved-sale-of-24-howitzers-to-qatar-bild-reports.html
Germany  plans to export 24
“Panzerhaubitze 2000” self-propelled howitzers to Qatar,  Bild-
Zeitung  reported, without saying how it got the information.  The country’s security council, then chaired by  Chancellor
Angela Merkel , approved the sale in 2009, the newspaper said.
The weapons are produced by  Rheinmetall AG (RHM)  and Krauss-Maffei
Wegmann GmbH, according to the report.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Cornelius Rahn in Frankfurt at 
 crahn2@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Kenneth Wong in Berlin at 
 kwong11@bloomberg.net  